name: I PROMISE TO FAIL | Object #3 : Coffee 1
description: This is the third of many single objects wrapped up with  the Brazilian cleaning tissue: Perfex. The concept of the work is based on the expectation of failure. The marketing promoted by the cleaning product promises perfection, absolute cleanliness and high-performance. However, its imminent failure is questioned as soon as its acetic superficiality comes into contact with its use. | video, 12' | 1080 x 1080 px | 14,9 MG - Twitter @erica__storer
